reviewText: But it is still possible to somewhat understand from the description, and just watching the images. One thing to note is that until the very last 15 minutes or so, the movie looks like a little bit better than what is shown on the scifi channels. i.e. the camera and special effects are a bit awkward, and fake looking at a lot of the times. But the last 20 minutes look really cool, a bit like dumbed down LOTR effects, but 30 times better than scifi channel special effects.
